item.title: Hamachi Question!
item.dc:creator: @curse63 curse63
item.description:
@curse63 wrote:

Do what you’ve done so far,click join after filling out the netowrk name and pass.
Then,go to the server ad thing were you see the info on the server.
Then fill in the server IP and port they give you.

Basically after you fill in the network name + pass on HAM,all you do is follow the normal things you do without HAM,but keep HAM running during the time your on the server.

[glow=red,2,300]IN A NUTSHELL VERSION OG THIS-IF YOU DONT WANA READ THE ABOVE,AND WANA BE QUIK! (BELOW)[/glow]

open HAM,type in net name + pass,go to the server add,fill in server Ip and the username+pass you wana use for that server.
